title: 2013 - The Year In Christian Music (Bundle 48)
description:
-----------------------------------------------------------------------
2013 - THE YEAR IN CHRISTIAN MUSIC
-----------------------------------------------------------------------

As the days continue to mount in 2013, and the year draws nearer to an end, I'm reminded of the 1,461 Christian music titles that we shared amongst ourselves back in 2012.  It's for this reason that I am pushing myself hard to surpass that total for 2013.  As of today, and including today's bundle, we've now shared 1,401 releases.  60 shy of 2012.  I would suspect that by the time we reach Bundle #50, we'll equal last years total.  Praise God!

CHRISTMAS: 714, For King And Country.  PRAISE & WORSHIP: Aaron Long, New City Music, Robby Cummings.  ROCK: Ali Crompton, The Fray, Matt Lynn.  ALTERNATIVE: Alter Bridge.  HARDCORE: And All Shall Bow, Crucial Moment, Vessels Of Veritas.  GOSPEL: Arthur Buckner, Eagle Rock Gospel Singers.  POP: City Harbor, Royal Tailor.  INSTRUMENTAL: Derrick Drover.  HIP-HOP/RAP: E-Sential, Hevn Li Angel, Jay-Rah, Lecrae, Milliyon, Nardo, Ohmega Watts, Rebuttal, Swae, Vita Christi, Yung Titus.   CONTEMPORARY: Jason Gray, Lacey Sturm, WoW Hits.  BLUES: The Sojourners, Tommy Ray.  INDIE: Warren Music.
